---
title: Tofu Curry and Crispy Chana Dal with Buttered Cilantro Rice
description: You'll be amazed at how much flavour is infused in this curry dish by marinating the tofu with herbs and spices, then cooking it in creamy Tikka sauce. To finish off this easy breezy meal, everything gets spooned over buttery cilantro rice and a sprinkle of crispy chana dal for extra flavour and crunch!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cari-de-tofu-et-chana-dal-croustillant-57ff2526.jpg
